cs.PL, cs.AR, cs.SE, cs.LG, cs.CE 

This paper proposes additional pragmas for loop transformations, which are commonly used in programming languages and compilers. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Programming Languages (cs.PL), Architecture (cs.AR), Software Engineering (cs.SE), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Computational Engineering (cs.CE) sub-categories.
